<Layout title="I'm Angry At Both — The Govt That Leaked NEET And The CJP That Used Us For FCRA | Vipul Zope" locked={false}>
  <div class="max-w-[700px] mx-auto px-6 py-8 sm:py-12">
    <h1 class="font-serif font-semibold text-[2rem] leading-[1.15] text-[var(--color-ink)] mb-2">i'm angry at both</h1>
    <p class="text-[1rem] leading-[1.5] text-[var(--color-ink-secondary)] mb-6">the govt that leaked NEET and the CJP that used us for FCRA</p>
    <p class="font-mono text-[0.6rem] tracking-[0.15em] uppercase text-[var(--color-ink-muted)] mb-10">20 Jul 2026</p>

    <div class="space-y-5 text-[0.95rem] leading-[1.7] text-[var(--color-ink-secondary)]">
      <p class="font-serif text-[1.3rem] font-semibold text-[var(--color-ink)] leading-[1.3]">the real timeline: NEET was the poster, FCRA was the agenda</p>
      <p class="font-mono text-[0.65rem] tracking-[0.08em] text-[var(--color-accent)] uppercase">this is not a student movement. this is a FCRA negotiation using student crowd.</p>

      <hr class="border-[var(--color-border)] my-6">

      <p class="font-serif text-[1.2rem] font-semibold text-[var(--color-ink)]">1. FCRA root — the real case</p>

      <p><strong class="text-[var(--color-ink)]">2007:</strong> First flag — Leh administration says Wangchuk misusing foreign funds.</p>

      <p><strong class="text-[var(--color-ink)]">2020-21:</strong> 5 transactions flagged — bus sale cash in foreign account, local volunteer money in foreign account, Sweden money for sovereignty study, return of foreign money, food fee cut.</p>

      <p>Wangchuk wants his foreign funding license back.</p>

      <p><strong class="text-[var(--color-ink)]">Aug 20, 2025:</strong> Show cause notice.</p>

      <p><strong class="text-[var(--color-ink)]">Sep 25, 2025:</strong> FCRA licence cancelled. CBI inquiry starts.</p>

      <p>Convicted? No. Only licence cancelled. But funding dead.</p>

      <p><strong class="text-[var(--color-ink)]">Mar 25, 2026:</strong> FCRA Amendment Bill introduced — can seize assets if FCRA lapses. This Bill is listed for Monsoon Session starting 20 July. This is what Wangchuk wants to negotiate.</p>

      <hr class="border-[var(--color-border)] my-6">

      <p class="font-serif text-[1.2rem] font-semibold text-[var(--color-ink)]">2. NEET leak — govt fails, then fixes</p>

      <p><strong class="text-[var(--color-ink)]">May 3, 2026:</strong> NEET 2026 leaks via NTA insider. Govt incompetent, true.</p>

      <p><strong class="text-[var(--color-ink)]">May 12, 2026:</strong> NEET cancelled, handed to CBI. Govt puts full focus on re-NEET.</p>

      <p><strong class="text-[var(--color-ink)]">June 21, 2026:</strong> Re-NEET done with max security — mock drills, enhanced surveillance, 22 lakh appeared. Leak fixed.</p>

      <p class="font-semibold text-[var(--color-ink)] text-[0.95rem]">June 21 — July 16 — the real govt process window:</p>

      <p>After re-NEET, Secretary + NTA DG + Ministry need detailed committees, rewrite SOPs, vendor rules, shift OMR to CBT, Cabinet approval. Takes 3-4 weeks. File was moving since May 12. That is why result took till July 16. Logical.</p>

      <p><strong class="text-[var(--color-ink)]">July 16, 2026:</strong> NEET UG 2026 Result declared — Official date.</p>

      <p class="font-semibold text-[var(--color-ink)] text-[0.95rem]">July 16 — July 20 — the 4-day fraud window you caught:</p>

      <p>Result came July 16. Immediately after, result challenge window opens. Some students submit fake AI-generated OMR sheets. NTA warns legal action. Small student-level fraud, not leak.</p>

      <p class="text-[var(--color-ink)] font-medium bg-[var(--color-accent-faint)] p-4 rounded-md border-l-3 border-[var(--color-accent)]">CJP play: They waited for July 16 result. They knew Day 1 Parliament July 20 is in 4 days where FCRA Bill will be listed. So they shout July 16-19 "See, still lapses, govt doing nothing." Then when govt announces SOPs/CBT reforms already decided since May 12, Wangchuk + Abhijeet will go live July 20-22 — "We won, our hunger strike forced govt."</p>

      <hr class="border-[var(--color-border)] my-6">

      <p class="font-serif text-[1.2rem] font-semibold text-[var(--color-ink)]">3. Acting + Pradhan drama</p>

      <p><strong class="text-[var(--color-ink)]">May 15:</strong> CJI says cockroach for fake degree youth. CJP gets brand.</p>

      <p><strong class="text-[var(--color-ink)]">May 16:</strong> CJP made by Abhijeet Dipke — ex-AAP social media volunteer, PR student Boston. Google Form party.</p>

      <p><strong class="text-[var(--color-ink)]">May 17 — July 16:</strong> 20M Instagram claim vs maximum 2k at Jantar Mantar including media. Online hype.</p>

      <p><strong class="text-[var(--color-ink)]">June 28:</strong> Hunger strike acting — Police shifts him to hospital, wife demands private hospital, court says not detained. Pure narrative acting through hunger strike.</p>

      <p>Cabinet rumour: Buzz that reshuffle due, Pradhan may be moved. No official order. CJP made primary demand "Resignation of Pradhan" using that rumour.</p>

      <p><strong class="text-[var(--color-ink)]">July 9:</strong> CJP announces Chalo Sansad on July 20.</p>

      <p><strong class="text-[var(--color-ink)]">July 20 Today:</strong> Day 1 of Monsoon Session — 20 July to 13 Aug, 7 Bills including FCRA Bill. You don't march on Day 1 for an exam already done. You march on Day 1 to negotiate FCRA.</p>

      <hr class="border-[var(--color-border)] my-6">

      <p class="font-serif text-[1.2rem] font-semibold text-[var(--color-ink)]">4. Support — fact checked</p>

      <p>No party officially backed CJP. Only low / FOMO individuals — Mahua Moitra, Kirti Azad, Akhilesh Yadav, Brinda Karat, Manish Sisodia, Prakash Raj. All photo-op.</p>

      <hr class="border-[var(--color-border)] my-6">

      <div class="bg-[var(--color-bg-deep)] p-5 rounded-md border-l-3 border-[var(--color-accent)]">
        <p class="text-[var(--color-ink)] font-semibold mb-2">final corrected dot in one line:</p>
        <p>Re-NEET June 21 fixed leak &rarr; Result July 16 &rarr; Only 4 days gap to Day 1 Parliament &rarr; Use AI OMR result frauds to keep anger alive &rarr; March July 20 to bargain FCRA + claim upcoming SOPs as your win.</p>
        <p class="mt-3">Yes, this govt is incompetent — it leaked NEET and wasted our year. But Wangchuk, Abhijeet and CJP are fraud — they knew govt fixed re-NEET with max security and needs weeks for SOPs, they knew FCRA Bill is on 20 July, so they used our anger, our AI OMR small lapses, our Pradhan anger, their hunger strike acting, to build a crowd for their FCRA negotiation. And they will frame govt's already-decided reforms as their win.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
